Usage: SPING [-clear] [<server>]
  Sends a ping to a server and displays the amount of time it took
  to go to the server and back.

  If no server is given, a list of servers which you are waiting for
  ping replies from is displayed.

  If the -clear argument is used, all currently pending server
  pings are removed from the queue.

See Also:
  PING
